	)
	(text "ESP32 Wroom 32 E datasheet p24 -> 3.3V pin needs one 22uF and one 100nF capacitors\n\nESP32 Devkit sch -> EN pin 10k resistor and 100nF capacitor\n\nESP32 Wroom 32 E datasheet p26 -> GND Thermal needs vias between pads. Needed vias are too small for my manufacturer. I will use bigger vias\n\nESP32 Devkit sch -> Automatic Bootloader.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 37.465 85.725 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2 2)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "95775086-63d6-410b-a7cb-9e187d4770b9")
	)
	(text "CP2102 datasheet p15 -> VBUS will be tied to REGIN. 1uF and 100 nF will be added.\nCP2102 datasheet p15 -> ESD Supression Diode for all three inputs of USB  \nCP2102 datasheet p15 and p19 -> 100nF for VDD output, 4.7 uF is optional for higher current circuits.\nCP2102 datasheet p23 -> The VDD or 3.3 output can only provide 100mA. I will not use this as a voltage provider for the ciruit. I will use the AMS1117-3.3 \nCP2102 datasheet p15 -> RST pulled up via 4.7k and SUSPEND~ pulled down via 10k."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 37.465 161.29 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2 2)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "b3a80b17-ff54-4c10-a24e-f68966c5e7c2")
	)
	(text "Filtering:\n\n\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 35.56 105.41 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2 2)
